title: Detective-Mystery Pulps A-Z
description:
This torrent contains all of the pulps and magazines we could find of the detective/mystery genre. This collection will be updated from time to time as more are scanned.

Filenames have been harmonized with Carlo's list (18 May 2014 version) and changes are noted in the "filename changes.txt" in individual magazine folders.
